{"tid":1735534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長盾製造（香城遊戲）","createTime":"2019-11-18T14:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T15:17:14.000Z","uid":128912,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6121ca25de81fa1099d317719d4261fc0e742315","tid":1735534,"uid":128912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGfftvA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGfftvA.jpg&h=78639c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nr0CGQC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNr0CGQC.jpg&h=e0ea1a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGiEaJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGiEaJY.jpg&h=2e5a58bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.將條木梯一分為二，上面連接點可以連住。（小心鐵釘）<br />\n2.上索帶加固，然後可以綁上街邊帆布或行李保鮮膜（最緊要確保有足夠彈性及韌性），例如禮義廉橫額，或直接綁上雨傘。大約要六把。<br />\n3.小心被打腳 。<br />\n<br />\n重量大約兩三公斤左右，一啲都唔重，但可以有完整防禦。<br />\n高度有1.6米左右。"},{"pid":"f9c6bf9c854afe61250385fecdb1248fbb90754d","tid":1735534,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00151e81c9c14857cde3f69d6ea82abb0bfd4bd","tid":1735534,"uid":128912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d20be772909dee0c3d706ea06b92a962c0f4c252","tid":1735534,"uid":128912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:01:57.000Z","msg":"朋友話係王甫世界都見到有三條木梯"},{"pid":"5a0629faf6115780018b9d5334949fd07ff0347e","tid":1735534,"uid":160363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"行李箱(打開)得唔得??"},{"pid":"1f85b577004b3e4ab0b238141f0958644c183ab1","tid":1735534,"uid":128912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a0629faf6115780018b9d5334949fd07ff0347e","tid":1735534,"uid":